      "content": "It sounds like you're feeling incredibly overwhelmed, and that your efforts aren't leading to the peace and acceptance you deserve. It's okay to take a step back and prioritize your well-being. Remember, your life has value and your struggles don't define you. While you might not know for sure yet, you don't have to go through this alone. Talking to a mental health professional can provide you with personalized support and tools to navigate through this challenging time. You're not alone, and it's okay to ask for help.",
      "source": "target",
